    /**
     *  Called by the transition to indicate that the transition
     *  has completed.
     *  This method dispatches the <code>end</code> event.
     * 
     *  @langversion 3.0
     *  @playerversion AIR 2.5
     *  @productversion Flex 4.5
     */
    protected function transitionComplete():void
